        pros: ['The systemic integration provides a highly frictionless experience, eliminating the context switching required by separate application usage', 'The "Private Cloud Compute" architecture establishes a verifiable, rigorous standard for consumer privacy in generative processing', 'The deep, personal contextual awareness (e.g., parsing relationships and schedules) enables highly specific utility unavailable to isolated, generalized models'],
