        pros: ['The unified API significantly mitigates the technical friction normally associated with testing numerous disparate AI models', 'Streaming fully interactive React components directly to the user introduces a substantially richer user experience compared to primitive text-based chatbots', 'Native optimization for Edge and Serverless environments aligns perfectly with modern, performance-oriented full-stack deployment frameworks'],
